      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, now you're saying the idea that gun control reduces crime is a \"flawed argument,\" but in your first message you said it was \"essential.\" so which one is it? are you saying the statistics are wrong or just that the law doesn't work? it feels like you're jumping back and forth.",
